.TEMP/

# Workspace-root lockfile should never exist — the root package.json declares
# no dependencies (it's just a scripts wrapper). A stray lockfile here tricks
# Next.js's workspace-root auto-detection into emitting .next/standalone/ to
# the wrong tree and breaks the VPS deploy. The only real lockfile lives at
# portfolio/package-lock.json.
/package-lock.json
